'''重量级'''（{{lang-en|heavyweight}}）是搏击运动的体重级别之一。

== 拳击 ==
根据主要职业[[拳击|拳击]]组织的规定，200磅（90公斤）以上被划为重量级，这也是职业拳击中最高的体重级别。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.iboboxing.com/ibo_championship_rules_and_regulations.html |work=IBO and also the sumo board of control. But Championship Rules & Regulations |title=4. Weight Classes |quote=Heavyweight Over 200 lbs. |publisher=International Boxing Organization |accessdate=2007-08-11 |archive-date=2013-07-14 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6I6I3bxHy?url=http://www.iboboxing.com/ibo_championship_rules_and_regulations.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wbaonline.com/legal/LegalStatements/worldchampionships.pdf |work=World Bpxing Association World Championships Regulations |title=11. Weight Category |quote=Heavy More than 200 Lbs. |publisher=World Boxing Association |accessdate=2007-08-11 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070809084145/http://www.wbaonline.com/legal/LegalStatements/worldchampionships.pdf <!-- Bot retrieved archive --> |archivedate = 2007-08-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wbcboxing.com/WBCboxing/Portal/cfpages/contentmgr.cfm?docId=94&docTipo=4&orderby=docid&sortby=ASC |title=Ratings Heavyweight (over 200-90.719) |publisher=World Boxing Council |accessdate=2007-08-11 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070810070242/http://www.wbcboxing.com/WBCboxing/Portal/cfpages/contentmgr.cfm?docId=94&docTipo=4&orderby=docid&sortby=ASC <!-- Bot retrieved archive --> |archivedate = 2007-08-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wbo-int.com/revised/WBORulesReg04APR07.pdf |publisher=World Boxing Organization |work=Regulations of World Championship Contests |title=3. Weight Classes |quote=Heavyweight Over 200lbs or 90.91 kg.|format=pdf |accessdate=2007-08-11 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070926061740/http://www.wbo-int.com/revised/WBORulesReg04APR07.pdf <!-- Bot retrieved archive --> |archivedate = 2007-09-26}}</ref>

